        <mxCell id="c4_assumptions" value="&lt;b&gt;Assumptions / Key Decisions&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Zero-secrets architecture: All service-to-service auth uses Managed Identity&lt;br&gt;• Microsoft Agent Framework (MAF) v1.0.0-rc3 with AIProjectClient pattern&lt;br&gt;• PostgreSQL used for both business data and job queue (no separate queue service)&lt;br&gt;• OpenTelemetry instrumentation on all containers&lt;br&gt;• 6 AI-enhanced agents use GPT-4 via AI Foundry&lt;br&gt;• 4 deterministic agents run rule-based analysis (no LLM calls)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF9C4;strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=10;" vertex="1" parent="c4_1">
