        <mxCell id="flow_maf_note" value="&lt;b&gt;Microsoft Agent Framework (MAF) Integration&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• AIProjectClient pattern for agent invocation&lt;br&gt;• Parallel execution: All 10 agents run concurrently&lt;br&gt;• Sequential coordination: Orchestrator → Agents → Aggregator&lt;br&gt;• Leader-worker: Orchestrator coordinates, agents execute independently&lt;br&gt;• Token streaming: GPT-4 responses streamed for real-time feedback&lt;br&gt;• Error handling: Individual agent failures don&apos;t block assessment&lt;br&gt;• Observability: OpenTelemetry traces track agent execution paths" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF9C4;strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=10;" vertex="1" parent="flow_1">
