        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="dep_security_note" value="&lt;b&gt;Security &amp; Compliance Highlights&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Managed Identities: All Container Apps use system-assigned identities&lt;br&gt;• Private Endpoints: PostgreSQL, Key Vault, ACR accessible only via VNet&lt;br&gt;• Network Security Perimeter: AI Foundry, AI Services in NSP learning mode&lt;br&gt;• Entra ID Authentication: PostgreSQL uses Entra ID (no SQL passwords)&lt;br&gt;• TLS Everywhere: HTTPS for external traffic, TLS 1.2+ for internal&lt;br&gt;• RBAC: Key Vault uses Azure RBAC (not access policies)&lt;br&gt;• Observability: OpenTelemetry → Log Analytics + App Insights&lt;br&gt;• Auto-scaling: Container Apps scale 1-10 replicas based on HTTP load&lt;br&gt;• Deployment: azd up with Bicep IaC (infrastructure/bicep/main.bicep)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF9C4;strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=10;" vertex="1" parent="dep_1">
